There’s a laundry list!

@jtwatkin @in_queue @ChiefsScott @thecallcenterc1 @theccdoctor @murphyjfraser @_Glenna_Mae @LukeCXEX @TomRichard11 @ddu17 @SeanBHawkins @dbeaumont266 @StossInSupport I think before even getting into the incentivized piece it starts with training &amp; comfort.

