@jennysuedempsey Take a few moments to disconnect! Walk away from the computer and grab some fresh air.

Use a lifeline and call a friend! 

Incorporate fun things into work that can help boost morale as well - things like “timesheet Friday aka memes galore!”

@jennysuedempsey @LeslieO @mrpatto @heycxguy Greeting of the day (E.g. Good Morning/Afternoon/Evening) + customer name.

Depending on the conversation it’ll be something personable/fun and then jumping into the reason behind the email/chat/call. I like the keep things fun and enjoyable in an interaction.

#cxqotd

@jennysuedempsey @jtwatkin @esmancuso @thatcxguytweets @CustomerIsFirst @justinmrobbins @JoshRaps Little late to the party but I’d go with FCR! 

